    "In this work, we carry out both binary and multi-class classification tasks in the experiments.",
    "For the binary classification problem, we predict the presence or absence of heart disease.",
    "For the four-class classification problem, we divide the labels into four unique classes to reflect various risk levels of heart disease.",
